entry.title: supervisor常用命令
entry.content: 启动服务 supervisorctld -c /etc/supervisorctld.conf 更新配置 supervisorctl update 重启 supervisorctl reload 启动 supervisorctl start app_name 停止 supervisorctl stop app_name 重新启动 supervisorctl restart app_name 全部停止 supervisorctl stop all
